= SDL_GetWindowPixelFormat =
Use this function to get the pixel format associated with the window.


== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint32 SDL_GetWindowPixelFormat(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the pixel format of the window on success, or ,,a negative error code,, ^an empty string^ on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

